to get out the game.

00:46.830 --> 00:48.410
That mean I'm in charge?

00:48.610 --> 00:49.380
Domino, motherfucker.

00:49.580 --> 00:51.700
[crowd screaming]

00:51.910 --> 00:53.550
<i>AVI:</i>
<i>You have to study everything</i>

00:53.750 --> 00:55.490
and travel.

00:55.680 --> 00:59.540
