01:47.240 --> 01:49.130
DODZI:
Gyata.

01:49.320 --> 01:50.560
Dodzi.

01:50.760 --> 01:52.850
- Dodzi, how are you?
- [replies in foreign language]

01:53.050 --> 01:55.680
What's up? I'm getting ready
to, uh, to drive my shift.

01:55.880 --> 01:56.910
Have you seen Wanda?

01:57.110 --> 01:59.260
Ah, did you look
on the other side of your bed?

01:59.460 --> 02:00.260
Of course, and she wasn't there.

02:00.460 --> 02:03.090
[both laugh]

02:03.290 --> 02:04.430
You sleep too long, man,

02:04.630 --> 02:06.060
and a beautiful lady like that
will get restless.

02:06.260 --> 02:07.700
She kept me dancing all night.

02:07.890 --> 02:09.400
- I had to get some kind of rest.
- [exclaims]

02:09.600 --> 02:12.150
[both laugh]

02:12.350 --> 02:14.790
But wait, um, Lumisi...

02:14.990 --> 02:16.880
she's at her sister's
fabric, uh, stall.

02:17.080 --> 02:18.570
- I think she might know.
- Cool, cool, appreciate it, man.

02:18.770 --> 02:20.160
[laughs] Wait, wait, wait,
one more thing, Gyata.

02:20.360 --> 02:23.990
Yeah, I saw Likem
at his sister's, um, herb stand.

02:24.190 --> 02:24.990
What'd that old man have to say?

02:25.190 --> 02:26.370
Uh, so he said

02:26.570 --> 02:28.340
it's-it's about time
to go to Almina.

02:28.540 --> 02:29.940
