02:40.670 --> 02:43.010
LEON:
Lumisi!

02:43.210 --> 02:45.160
Gyata.

02:46.160 --> 02:47.480
That was a pretty good sale

02:47.680 --> 02:49.050
- you made me lose back there.
- Sorry, I'm sorry.

02:49.250 --> 02:50.650
- Look, look,
I'm looking for Wanda.
- Yeah.

02:50.850 --> 02:52.310
- And Dodzi said you might
know where she is.
- I do. I do.

02:52.510 --> 02:54.270
- Take me, take me.
- Come with me.

02:57.830 --> 02:59.930
