03:35.780 --> 03:38.350
Okay, I love this
for my grandma.

03:38.560 --> 03:39.530
Oh, that's nice.

03:39.730 --> 03:40.930
- Right?
- This is nice.

03:41.130 --> 03:43.700
Yeah, and then look
how it looks on.

03:43.910 --> 03:45.360
I don't know,
it might even be for you,

03:45.560 --> 03:46.530
- 'cause that looks good on you.
- [laughs]

03:46.740 --> 03:50.670
