04:40.970 --> 04:42.970
Oh, ah... [hisses]

04:44.690 --> 04:47.040
Ah...

04:47.240 --> 04:49.200
Two, please.

04:49.400 --> 04:50.420
Yes.

04:55.150 --> 04:57.220
