05:35.410 --> 05:37.120
I don't want to go.

05:38.130 --> 05:39.640
I don't.

05:42.340 --> 05:43.270
Lee.

05:43.470 --> 05:45.480
Everything's moving so fast,
you know.

05:45.680 --> 05:46.650
Yeah.

05:46.860 --> 05:48.790
There's nothing
back there for me.

05:52.800 --> 05:56.210
Just... look at our people.

05:57.800 --> 06:01.220
Look at how beautiful and free.

06:02.250 --> 06:06.290
And then here we can be
whoever we want to be.

06:07.670 --> 06:12.330
Not our past,
not our stuff we've done.

06:13.920 --> 06:15.990
But who we really are in here.

06:16.200 --> 06:18.230
People see us.

06:20.200 --> 06:23.990
We're not back
getting chased by cops

06:24.190 --> 06:27.070
or shot in the back by friends.

06:28.240 --> 06:30.560
Let's just stay here.

06:36.110 --> 06:37.970
I hear everything
you're saying to me

06:38.160 --> 06:40.240
and I feel
exactly what you feel.

06:40.440 --> 06:42.540
No, Lee, you don't know.

06:42.740 --> 06:44.110
But I have to think about it.

06:44.310 --> 06:46.160
I love it here, too.

06:46.360 --> 06:47.940
I feel free, I...

06:48.140 --> 06:49.580
Trust me.

06:51.510 --> 06:54.000
