12:47.100 --> 12:48.650
Okay, but if I do that,

12:48.850 --> 12:49.990
I got to go back to get my money

12:50.190 --> 12:52.180
and set up some kind
of system anyway.

12:53.490 --> 12:56.270
They just want
to destroy us, Lee.

12:56.470 --> 12:57.790
They want us in jail,

12:57.990 --> 12:59.860
they want to kill us.

13:00.060 --> 13:01.690
- They want to break
up our families.
- Look, look, Wanda,

13:01.890 --> 13:03.780
I can't do this without you.

13:13.410 --> 13:15.890
