[laughs]:
Come sit.

20:43.280 --> 20:44.690
Franklin, how are you?

20:44.890 --> 20:46.590
Fine, thank you.

20:48.100 --> 20:50.040
Y'all two look like
you're having fun.

20:50.240 --> 20:51.840
Yeah, we're having a great time.

20:52.040 --> 20:54.130
Glad to hear it.

20:54.330 --> 20:57.560
So, um, I take it
that means we all set?

20:57.770 --> 21:00.340
Tomorrow at lunch.
He will be out of the office,

21:00.540 --> 21:02.430
and his files
will be in our hands.

21:04.470 --> 21:05.350
Good.

21:05.550 --> 21:08.590
One more thing, <i>beau-fils.</i>

21:08.790 --> 21:10.840
Thank you.

21:11.040 --> 21:14.440
For bringing this beautiful
creature back into my life.

21:32.730 --> 21:34.390
LOUIE:
Sorry.

21:35.630 --> 21:37.230
Was riding,

21:37.430 --> 21:39.140
lost track of time.

21:39.340 --> 21:41.120
[camera shutter clicking]

21:51.890 --> 21:53.850
I understand.

21:54.050 --> 21:55.230
Uh, two adult males.

21:55.430 --> 21:58.070
Call it, um, 50 pounds cargo.

21:59.420 --> 22:00.280
[door opens]

22:00.480 --> 22:02.580
Mm-hmm, confirmed.

22:02.780 --> 22:03.860
[door closes]

22:04.060 --> 22:06.290
Wheels up, 0400.

22:07.530 --> 22:08.810
Thank you.

22:12.980 --> 22:14.190
How'd the deal go?

22:15.610 --> 22:16.810
GUSTAVO:
Good.

22:17.780 --> 22:19.190
How'd Louie seem?

22:20.510 --> 22:22.160
Same as always.

22:24.230 --> 22:26.930
So, listen, I need you here
at 3:00 in the morning.

22:28.690 --> 22:30.430
Why?

22:30.630 --> 22:31.800
Uh, we're going to Costa Rica.

22:32.000 --> 22:32.800
GUSTAVO:
Costa...

22:33.000 --> 22:36.590
Costa Rica? Tomorrow?

22:41.630 --> 22:43.550
For how long?

22:43.750 --> 22:45.770
I don't know, a day. Maybe two.

22:50.570 --> 22:52.610
[indistinct chatter]

22:52.810 --> 22:54.030
[spits]

22:54.230 --> 22:56.940
- [distant sirens wailing]
- [motorcycle revving]

22:57.140 --> 22:58.820
[dog barking]

23:04.410 --> 23:07.400
[distant chatter continues]

23:07.600 --> 23:09.130
[baby crying]

23:09.330 --> 23:11.010
[woman shouting indistinctly]

23:13.840 --> 23:15.270
Lee?

23:15.470 --> 23:17.140
Hey, man, when'd you get back?

23:17.340 --> 23:18.880
Not too long ago.

23:20.220 --> 23:22.500
- That's a nice jacket
you got there.
- Appreciate it.

23:28.260 --> 23:30.290
